'From Squeak3.6beta of ''4 July 2003'' [latest update: #5331] on 10 July 2003 at 5:27:40 pm'!"Change Set:		TTCFontPixelSizeFix-nkDate:			10 July 2003Author:			Ned KonzThis fixes the walkbacks caused by using TTCFonts in point sizes that didn't equate to integer pixel sizes."!!TTCFont methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'nk 7/10/2003 17:27'!height	"Answer my height in pixels. This will answer a Float."	^ self pixelSize! !!TTCFont methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'nk 7/10/2003 15:55'!pixelSize	"Make sure that we don't return a Fraction"	^ pointSize * 96.0 / 72.0.! !